text: Maurice Jacquel (14 March 1929 - 10 April 2004) was a French wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:2004 deaths Category:French male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of France Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vosges (department)
